<salute>Dear Mr. Meehan, </salute>
<p>I am desired by Mr. Birrell to acknowledge the <lb/>
receipt of your letter of the 3rd instant recommending <lb/>
Mr. Delany for appointment as Chief Crown Solicitor for <lb/>
Ireland, and to say that Mr. Birrell has taken a note <lb/>
of your recommendation of Mr. Delany.</p>
<salute>Yours faithfully,</salute>
(Sd.) A.P.M<lb/>
Under Secretary<lb/>
A.P.M<lb/>
<date>4/4/16</date>

